  "title": "Service Technician (Crane)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a MNC in Equipment Manufacturing sector. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Maintenance &amp; Service Technician to be part of their Sales team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the West – easily accessible.</strong></p>\n<p>Responsibilities of <strong>Maintenance &amp; Service Technician</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintain and repair company and third-party equipment.</li>\n  <li>Ensuring top performance via inspections and routine maintenance.</li>\n  <li>Deliver excellent customer service with detailed reports and technical advice.</li>\n  <li>Ensure a safe work environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum ITE in engineering field</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1 years of machinery maintenance and troubleshooting experience</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>\n<p><strong>Email: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p>\n<p>RecruitPedia Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 19C9682</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
